    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I am sorry to interrupt the hon. Gentleman, but we are, of course, discussing the Army Estimates, and what he says must be relevant to the Army Estimates.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a2481570-1568-4663-b472-2fd9af00302f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1939-03-14/debates/da568d07-f2de-468b-b233-0ca836031e1c/Army(RoyalOrdnanceFactories)SupplementaryEstimate1938#contribution-a2481570-1568-4663-b472-2fd9af00302f">
