<p class="">Was that the Regular Army?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-7057b3c8-0ad9-498f-9a9a-6b1cd70843fe" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
