<p class="">I do not understand my hon. and gallant Friend. We are producing this gun in our own factory in thousands, and equipping all the Regular battalions completely. This is not a gun which we have imported; it is a gun that we are manufacturing here.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
