        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My right hon. Friend said he would send in writing some of the <span id="322" class="column-number" data-column-number="322"></span> rather important points. Will he send that information on paper?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
